sequenceDiagram
    participant Creator as FE (Creator)
    participant IPFS
    participant Wallet
    participant SC as Smart Contract
    participant BE as Backend Indexer
    participant DB as Database

    Note over Creator: User fills form (Title, Img, etc.)
    Creator->>IPFS: Upload JSON Metadata
    IPFS-->>Creator: Return CID (string)
    
    Creator->>Wallet: createCampaign(goal, deadline, CID)
    Wallet->>SC: Transaction: createCampaign
    activate SC
    SC->>SC: Validate inputs
    SC->>SC: CampaignCount++
    SC-->>BE: Emit Event: CampaignCreated
    deactivate SC
    
    Note over BE: Listens to event
    BE->>DB: INSERT into campaigns (status=ACTIVE)
    BE->>IPFS: (Optional) Fetch Metadata details
    BE->>DB: Update Title/Category columns
    
    Creator->>BE: GET /campaigns
    BE-->>Creator: Returns new campaign list
